dcterms:description: The So2Sat LCZ42 dataset consists of LCZ labels for approximately half a million Sentinel-1 (EO) and Sentinel-2 (SAR) satellite image patches over 42 cities across the world, labeled with one of 17 total classes (ten urban zone types, seven natural zone types).
dcterms:title: So2Sat LCZ42

dcterms:description: Sentinel-1 and Sentinel-2 satellite imagery used for analysis and transfer learning in the context of land use and climate zone classification.
dcterms:title: Sentinel-1 (EO) and Sentinel-2 (SAR)
